4
00:00:14.347 --> 00:00:15.682
- [Wes] This is our area.
- It's not.

5
00:00:15.765 --> 00:00:16.975
Back your ass up.

6
00:00:17.058 --> 00:00:19.060
[intense drumbeat builds]

7
00:00:23.398 --> 00:00:24.691
[tense music resumes]

8
00:00:25.692 --> 00:00:27.861
