13
00:00:39.080 --> 00:00:41.041
I ain't talking to you.
I got my eye on this one.

14
00:00:45.754 --> 00:00:49.466
{\an8}It's just so frustrating when someone
knows how to get under your skin.

15
00:00:49.549 --> 00:00:53.053
