64
00:04:01.741 --> 00:04:03.409
This is definitely. like…

65
00:04:04.953 --> 00:04:05.995
the monster's lair.

66
00:04:06.079 --> 00:04:09.415
It's really beat down with tracks in here.

67
00:04:10.750 --> 00:04:12.001
Multiple trails.

68
00:04:13.169 --> 00:04:15.755
